<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PTM6.4.9">
<l>kaṉicērn tilaṅku nalvāyavar kātaṉmai viṭṭiṭa</l>
<l>kuṉicērn tuṭalam kōlilta ḷarntiḷai yātamuṉ</l>
<l>paṉicēr vicumpil pāṉmati kōḷviṭut tāṉiṭam</l>
<l>naṉicēr naṟaiyūr nāmtoḻu tummeḻu neñcamē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Before my body can grow thin, acquiring a hump, drooping on a staff,</l>
<l>So that those with fine, shining lips like fruit</l>
<l rend="indent">completely abandon affection [for me],</l>
<l>Arise, [my] heart! We will worship in excellent Naṟaiyūr, the place of the one</l>
<l>Who split the serpent of the milky moon in the misty sky.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
